Parameters

  • color (str, optional) – color of the line, defaults to ‘’

  • ls (str, optional) – Style of the line, defaults to ‘-‘

  • label (str, optional) – Label for the line, defaults to ‘’

  • length (int, optional) – Length of the line, defaults to 50

  • numberOfXs (int, optional) – number of x-values, defaults to 50

  • shiftInX (int, optional) – Shift the line along x-axis, defaults to None

  • draw (bool, optional) – draw the plot to screen, defaults to True

  • _return (bool, optional) – return the xs, ys, x-min and x-max, defaults to False

Returns

tuple of lists if _return == True
